::KitKat::

She ran along with Rowdy and Terrorsaur.  She reopened her link again 
since she got no acknowlagement from Quickstrike the first time.

"Commander Quickstrike, Terrorsaur and I found Rowdy and we are on 
our way back to base Sir.  We shall arrive shortly. KitKat out."

She hoped that Quickstrike would be at the base when they got there.
